	<h1 class="title">在教堂里睡一个晚上，是英国最新露营方式</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/37535/small/37535.jpg?1425436713" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">魏思静</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-03-26 10:06:10 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/7780/medium/7780.jpg?1436693484" alt="" />			
	</div>
